  "text": "The diagnosis of HCC is mostly based on imaging studies and laboratory tests as well. The imaging studies used in diagnosis, treatment planning, management and follow-up of HCC are ultrasonography (US), computed tomography (CT) scanning and magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) [CITATION_1] (Figure 1 ).",
